00:19:35.460 --> 00:19:38.860
You don't have to take a chance or
a risk, which is sort of symbolic

00:19:38.860 --> 00:19:42.600
of what I was trying to say about
getting out of your comfort zone.

00:19:42.600 --> 00:19:44.570
It's almost like in the
universe saying, you know,

00:19:44.570 --> 00:19:48.720
