hundred thousand trillion planets

00:19:48.720 --> 00:19:52.050
that might have life on it so
we should just stay where we are

00:19:52.050 --> 00:19:54.270
because it will be safe here.

00:19:54.270 --> 00:19:57.640
Vega Jane realizes everything
she's been told in life is a lie --

00:19:57.640 --> 00:20:00.100
everything -- about Wormwood,
the people that live there,

00:20:00.100 --> 00:20:01.400
their history, everything.

00:20:01.400 --> 00:20:04.980
So she breaks out of Wormwood and
