00:20:40.250 --> 00:20:43.080
because Vega kept escaping
from places.

00:20:43.080 --> 00:20:45.440
So The Finisher was Wormwood.

00:20:45.440 --> 00:20:47.210
The Keeper was the Quag.

00:20:47.210 --> 00:20:49.030
And now in, The Width
of the World, it was --

00:20:49.030 --> 00:20:50.430
she had broken free from the Quag,

00:20:50.430 --> 00:20:52.360
