the industry puts on this book,

00:21:45.360 --> 00:21:47.190
that meant nothing to me.

00:21:47.190 --> 00:21:51.700
All I know is that I was going
to be writing for myself but also

00:21:51.700 --> 00:21:56.410
for really smart people out
there who probably read a lot

00:21:56.410 --> 00:22:01.070 position:56%
of fantasy regardless of whether
